	<body>
		<outline text="July 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="july2021" >
			<outline text="July 16" type="calendarDay" name="16" >
				<outline text="TIL the Social Register has a website &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.socialregisteronline.com/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 14:50:04 GMT" tweetId="1416047488268636165" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1416047488268636165" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is good &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/broderick/status/1416030550033371143&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 14:13:08 GMT" tweetId="1416038192470446082" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1416038192470446082" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="“office bod”??? &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/bw/status/1415872901627236354&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 12:59:04 GMT" tweetId="1416019555059736580" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1416019555059736580" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Follow me on IG!!! 🙏🏻 &lt;a href=&quot;https://instagram.com/taylorlorenz/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/Askh9l0cCd" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 12:43:47 GMT" tweetId="1416015705070350343" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1416015705070350343" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 15" type="calendarDay" name="15" >
				<outline text="These stories of #longcovid are horrifying. I hope those suffering get the treatment and acknowledgment they deserve. Scary how dismissive our systems can be to those who are disabled or suffer w/ chronic illness &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-57693637&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 03:15:05 GMT" tweetId="1415872590095204353" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415872590095204353" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="My child &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/adet0la/status/1415770805452120067&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 02:45:52 GMT" tweetId="1415865238210158592" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415865238210158592" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Buried scoop: Virgil Abloh is building a virtual clothing brand for clothes to wear in the metaverse. 

&quot;I want to make virtual clothes to paint pictures physical clothes cannot, and let buyers access a new dimension of their personal style&quot; Mr. Abloh said &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.matthewball.vc/all/csametaverse&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:53:42 GMT" tweetId="1415776611580928006" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415776611580928006" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Abloh has been really into NFTs, back in February he said, &quot;the real world is just the part-time metaverse.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CLwtSDEpsBO/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:55:35 GMT" tweetId="1415777086283862022" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415777086283862022" inReplyToId="1415776611580928006" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Sounds about right &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/MikaelThalen/status/1415764784067186688&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:31:10 GMT" tweetId="1415770939799842821" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415770939799842821" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="&quot;The notion of a special bond with a creator is contrived, and what seems like unfettered access to their lives is curated. It’s the intimacy you’d get from any imaginary friend.&quot; Fantastic piece by @fadeke_adegbuyi on parasocial relationships &lt;a href=&quot;https://every.to/cybernaut/the-blurred-lines-of-parasocial-relationships&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:29:41 GMT" tweetId="1415770566242545667" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415770566242545667" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is how we win 🔥 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/criterion/status/1415710012442296324&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 17:15:07 GMT" tweetId="1415721603007197186" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415721603007197186" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="A thread by the co-creator of dogecoin. Interested to hear people's thoughts here &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ummjackson/status/1415353984617914370&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 16:01:25 GMT" tweetId="1415703053555150849" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415703053555150849" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Found this thread very interesting &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/evan_greer/status/1415640716357906433&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 22:59:38 GMT" tweetId="1415808300936044544" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415808300936044544" inReplyToId="1415703053555150849" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text=".@NoahShachtman is intense and fearless and I will always be indebted to him for giving me my first full time reporting job. Respect to him always and congrats on the new gig, everyone at Rolling Stone is very lucky 🔥&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/15/business/rolling-stone-new-editor.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 15:40:26 GMT" tweetId="1415697773425483777" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415697773425483777" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Middle-aged mums &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-9786635/Middle-aged-MUMS-likely-troll-social-media-influencers.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 15:20:04 GMT" tweetId="1415692648422285312" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415692648422285312" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="The whole &quot;leaving SF&quot; thing was just about the RTs for so many ppl &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/15/technology/tech-workers-bay-area-back.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 15:08:21 GMT" tweetId="1415689700233318404" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415689700233318404" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 14" type="calendarDay" name="14" >
				<outline text="Amazing job alert 🚨 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/whoweekly/status/1415320691348492295&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 02:34:33 GMT" tweetId="1415499999283142657" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415499999283142657" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Declaring text bankruptcy &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1415455432487886854/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 23:37:27 GMT" tweetId="1415455432487886854" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415455432487886854" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is really interesting &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/boztank/status/1415416877560565764&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 21:06:38 GMT" tweetId="1415417475639005184" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415417475639005184" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I think the key phrase here is journalistic standards. There's absolutely an opportunity for a more traditional entertainment/news brand to capture that space &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/kelsaywhat/status/1415374573416112131&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 18:53:50 GMT" tweetId="1415384056884301825" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415384056884301825" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Once again, they should just allow regular tweets to expire! &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/verge/status/1415361369348640771&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 17:26:26 GMT" tweetId="1415362062214119425" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415362062214119425" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Twitter says that influencer news page Def Noodles has been permanently suspended  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businessinsider.com/def-noodles-twitter-banned-suspended-why-violating-rules-2021-7&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 16:21:52 GMT" tweetId="1415345814663319561" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415345814663319561" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="EXCLUSIVE: Facebook plans to pay creators $1 billion to use its products. The payouts are part of a broader effort to woo influencers onto its platforms &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/14/technology/facebook-payments-creators.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 16:20:09 GMT" tweetId="1415345380913524743" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415345380913524743" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="The $1 billion will be allocated among creators of all types, giving influencers an incentive for creating and posting original content to Facebook &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/14/technology/facebook-payments-creators.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 16:22:32 GMT" tweetId="1415345980560580612" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415345980560580612" inReplyToId="1415345380913524743" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="Creators can earn money by using specific Facebook and Instagram features or by hitting certain milestones/metrics. If a creator live streams on a regular basis, for instance, they can earn cash. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/14/technology/facebook-payments-creators.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 16:23:08 GMT" tweetId="1415346130687348739" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415346130687348739" inReplyToId="1415345980560580612" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="Had a blast breaking down the Call Her Daddy $60M deal and what it means for the creator ecosystem w/ the goats @ColinandSamir! &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ColinandSamir/status/1415309232602161156&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 15:47:21 GMT" tweetId="1415337126191898625" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415337126191898625" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="TikTok Becomes the First Non-Facebook Mobile App to Reach 3 Billion Downloads Globally &lt;a href=&quot;https://sensortower.com/blog/tiktok-downloads-3-billion&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 15:22:22 GMT" tweetId="1415330839689408515" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415330839689408515" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I want to meet the person Spotify thinks I am &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1415308061305155584/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 13:51:51 GMT" tweetId="1415308061305155584" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415308061305155584" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is really terrifying, hope everyone stays safe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/society/2021/jul/13/delta-surge-could-leave-hundreds-of-thousands-with-long-covid&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 10:23:57 GMT" tweetId="1415255741720563712" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415255741720563712" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 13" type="calendarDay" name="13" >
				<outline text="Anyone on here seriously love/miss working from an office and/or thinking about quitting their job if it stays remote only??" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 22:38:27 GMT" tweetId="1415078195259486214" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415078195259486214" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="*please read my tweet, I am not advocating this, I'm just wondering if anyone feels this way! I know there must be some die hard office lovers out there." type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 23:02:47 GMT" tweetId="1415084321921187840" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415084321921187840" inReplyToId="1415078195259486214" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="DefNoodles, a popular drama/tea account that documents influencer news, is currently suspended &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/banishedjourno/status/1415064280664137728&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 22:29:30 GMT" tweetId="1415075943438340099" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415075943438340099" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is an awesome gig I would have jumped at when I was freelance! Check it out &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/markyarm/status/1415010763031339022&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 22:16:24 GMT" tweetId="1415072648418242563" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415072648418242563" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Another absolutely wild story by @IAmAsarch &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/iamasarch/status/1415049836387348481&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 21:01:37 GMT" tweetId="1415053827225554949" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415053827225554949" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text=".@IAmAsarch has an expert ability to break down niche community drama &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businessinsider.com/bbw-pearadise-body-postive-tiktok-stefan-wilhelmy-sue-women-defamation-2021-7&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 21:03:03 GMT" tweetId="1415054189017894919" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415054189017894919" inReplyToId="1415053827225554949" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="I mean sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/brobible/status/1415044940128825345&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 21:00:30 GMT" tweetId="1415053547142623237" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415053547142623237" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Companies don't want to pay overtime, then they also don't want to give you extra time off for the amount of work it takes to get a job done. @edzitron on how burnout is not a mental health issue, it is an organizational issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://ez.substack.com/p/the-burnout-conversation-is-a-corporate&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 20:34:16 GMT" tweetId="1415046945081643009" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415046945081643009" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="@edzitron &quot;The cause of burnout is too much work, and the solution to too much work is to make sure people have more time to do their work OR add more people so that they have less work to do.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://ez.substack.com/p/the-burnout-conversation-is-a-corporate&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 20:36:21 GMT" tweetId="1415047469042479109" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415047469042479109" inReplyToId="1415046945081643009" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="This video plays in my head once a day &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/calebsaysthings/status/1365776466810605569&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 16:47:01 GMT" tweetId="1414989755629117446" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414989755629117446" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is why I had to leave DC 😌 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ryanbeckwith/status/1414977704819105794&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 16:03:34 GMT" tweetId="1414978820529082382" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414978820529082382" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Jk it was to finally escape @swin24" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 16:19:25 GMT" tweetId="1414982807466790920" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414982807466790920" inReplyToId="1414978820529082382" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="DC people are always on a 5 year culture delay &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/rubycramer/status/1414973101092315140&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 15:56:23 GMT" tweetId="1414977014101168130" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414977014101168130" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="For those just learning about Olivia Rodrigo definitley check out @joecoscarelli's great Diary of a Song w/ her! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/arts/music/olivia-rodrigo-drivers-license.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 16:01:27 GMT" tweetId="1414978286904619013" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414978286904619013" inReplyToId="1414977014101168130" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="FYI: Tons of young influencers have been doing videos with Fauci and creating content w/ the White House encouraging people to get vaccinated. Tinx did one recently too! &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/jeneps/status/1414962370783363074&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 15:55:33 GMT" tweetId="1414976801277894659" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414976801277894659" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I spy @joshgondelman @jerm_cohen  the Green Lady and more on this @brooklynmag list of the 50 most fascinating people in Brooklyn &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bkmag.com/brooklyns-50-most-fascinating/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 15:35:02 GMT" tweetId="1414971639096348684" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414971639096348684" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text=".@brooklynmag's 50 most fascinating people in Brooklyn is out! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bkmag.com/brooklyns-50-most-fascinating/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 15:31:47 GMT" tweetId="1414970821358112771" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414970821358112771" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 12" type="calendarDay" name="12" >
				<outline text="One of the 2010's most pivotal moments in cultural history. We will never be the same &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/broderick/status/1414688305300578308&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 21:04:06 GMT" tweetId="1414692065947136007" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414692065947136007" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/bijanstephen/status/1414690876534755340&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 21:22:23 GMT" tweetId="1414696667333414916" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414696667333414916" inReplyToId="1414692065947136007" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="I'm at the restaurant. I'm at the stock market. I'm at the combination restaurant and stock market. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/janiraplanes/status/1414688060139360258&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 20:49:57 GMT" tweetId="1414688501833084931" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414688501833084931" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Pretty sure the Science desk has the best headline writers in the newsroom. @michaelroston how can we compete!? 😅 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/09/science/cuttlefish-cognition-cephalopods.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 20:49:09 GMT" tweetId="1414688304000294912" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414688304000294912" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Just me trying to keep up with you!!! 😅 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/kyurieff/status/1414680636095401992&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 20:31:52 GMT" tweetId="1414683953211101186" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414683953211101186" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="“People’s worst fears about the app come true.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/lmatsakis/status/1414600925453459462&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 18:31:24 GMT" tweetId="1414653637800964096" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414653637800964096" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Had a great time teaming up with @MikeIsaac on this one! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/facebook-creators-tiktok-youtube.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 18:08:40 GMT" tweetId="1414647913347698699" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414647913347698699" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is true! I’ve never been a great writer, but if you’re excellent at uncovering new information and reporting things out, you don’t have to be the most beautiful writer in the room.☺️ &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/bonazoulay/status/1414603521467498497&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 15:18:17 GMT" tweetId="1414605036626268161" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414605036626268161" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="&quot;Isn’t the world much more exciting now that Caroline Calloway could be waiting inside any given bar, waiting to pour Snake Oil on your face?&quot; @kathrynfiona  &lt;a href=&quot;https://embedded.substack.com/p/some-news-our-paid-launch-caroline&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:52:49 GMT" tweetId="1414598627956244484" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414598627956244484" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I just paid to subscribe to @getembedded and you should too! It's an absolutely essential and really thoughtful newsletter on internet culture and the online creator world &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/kathrynfiona/status/1414597517778489346&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:51:49 GMT" tweetId="1414598375442419719" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414598375442419719" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="So cool to see this little ~creator economy~ box of my stories on NYT dot com!! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/content-creators-venture-capital.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/00K0VMxLcc" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:42:08 GMT" tweetId="1414595938556026882" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414595938556026882" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I wrote about the consumer investing boom driven by the rise of the &quot;creator economy&quot;, how VCs are embracing the online creator world and what that means for the industry. w/ @erinkwoo  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/content-creators-venture-capital.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:31:07 GMT" tweetId="1414593165764579334" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414593165764579334" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Read me and @erinkwoo story on how VCs are going wild for creators! 

“I’ve seen a few posts from V.C.s saying, ‘Eight of the 10 companies I met with today are creator companies. It really is en vogue now.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/content-creators-venture-capital.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:33:38 GMT" tweetId="1414593802019409925" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414593802019409925" inReplyToId="1414593165764579334" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="@erinkwoo “There are more creator economy start-ups than creators,” @TurnerNovak, founder of Banana Capital, which invests in early-stage tech start-ups, joked. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/content-creators-venture-capital.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:34:08 GMT" tweetId="1414593926883913736" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414593926883913736" inReplyToId="1414593802019409925" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
							<outline text="@erinkwoo @TurnerNovak The word “creator” has become a buzzword in the VC/startup world, appended to all types of businesses to attract investors. So much so that @alexfinden, a tech entrepreneur, coined the term “creator washing.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/content-creators-venture-capital.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:35:07 GMT" tweetId="1414594172271607810" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414594172271607810" inReplyToId="1414593926883913736" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
								<outline text="@erinkwoo @TurnerNovak @alexfinden “Older social platforms, those were all about interacting with your friends online,” said @LinusWalton, vice president at the Chernin Group. Now “it’s all about becoming that influencer, or becoming that new TikTok star that all your friends are watching.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/content-creators-venture-capital.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:37:19 GMT" tweetId="1414594727484301313" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414594727484301313" inReplyToId="1414594172271607810" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
									<outline text="“For years, no one cared or recognized this space as a space with real money. Now, with money pouring into the industry, we’re only going to see more companies, more competition and more start-ups involving creators as a part of their businesses.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/content-creators-venture-capital.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:38:56 GMT" tweetId="1414595132318486530" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414595132318486530" inReplyToId="1414594727484301313" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
									</outline>
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="I’m back baby &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1414587156165713925/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:07:14 GMT" tweetId="1414587156165713925" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414587156165713925" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="First NYT bathroom selfie in over a year 🥰 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1414606056064442370/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 15:22:20 GMT" tweetId="1414606056064442370" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414606056064442370" inReplyToId="1414587156165713925" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Absolute legends here 👇🏻 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sheeraf/status/1414585818308567041&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 14:06:16 GMT" tweetId="1414586912300482561" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414586912300482561" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I wrote about Facebook’s (very late) efforts to court creators w/ @MikeIsaac &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/12/technology/facebook-creators-tiktok-youtube.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 13:03:30 GMT" tweetId="1414571116144828421" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414571116144828421" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="👇🏻 Just educating creators on their product is going to be important as FB pushes into this space &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/kevinbparry/status/1414573406339706881&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 12 Jul 2021 13:14:22 GMT" tweetId="1414573852869505024" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414573852869505024" inReplyToId="1414571116144828421" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 10" type="calendarDay" name="10" >
				<outline text="“Reality TV but MORE real with MORE content, 24/7” is a good way to describe what the internet has become as creators become more dominate. Another good breakdown by @kattenbarge &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/kattenbarge/status/1413929235262197766&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 10 Jul 2021 18:46:28 GMT" tweetId="1413932654098059269" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413932654098059269" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="The quote tweets on this are wild, it’s very common to get a celeb to do red carpet Qs! This takes place often at award shows and other events. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/whoisaddison/status/1413656072678641664&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 10 Jul 2021 12:54:03 GMT" tweetId="1413843965237997569" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413843965237997569" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="A celeb asking some easy Qs on the red carpet is not “stealing jobs from those more deserving.” It is their celebrity/fame that qualifies them for that type of opportunity. Having a famous person ask other famous people Qs is a tactic to build buzz and get people to watch" type="tweet" created="Sat, 10 Jul 2021 12:56:50 GMT" tweetId="1413844665762254851" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413844665762254851" inReplyToId="1413843965237997569" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="Exactly &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/mohamadtm91/status/1413844826760519683&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 10 Jul 2021 12:58:12 GMT" tweetId="1413845009728741376" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413845009728741376" inReplyToId="1413844665762254851" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
							<outline text="Yup this too &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/mohamadtm91/status/1413845757141024771&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 10 Jul 2021 13:03:51 GMT" tweetId="1413846429911691269" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413846429911691269" inReplyToId="1413845009728741376" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
								<outline text="I think some ppl aren’t aware of how woven into the media ecosystem influencers are. Having over 120M followers across platforms does qualify someone for opportunities like this b/c they’re being hired in a promotional capacity. This is stuff I wish journalism schools would teach &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/mtzler/status/1413850796458917891&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 10 Jul 2021 13:28:02 GMT" tweetId="1413852516526272512" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413852516526272512" inReplyToId="1413846429911691269" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 9" type="calendarDay" name="09" >
				<outline text="This is amazing, what a great team @BostonJoan has assembled! &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/JaneLytv/status/1413586949722492928&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 19:55:39 GMT" tweetId="1413587674099855360" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413587674099855360" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Why not both! 😌 @broderick &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1413535590251892739/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 16:28:41 GMT" tweetId="1413535590251892739" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413535590251892739" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="What season of Succession is this &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/oliverdarcy/status/1413503572906369033&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 14:37:49 GMT" tweetId="1413507690257473536" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413507690257473536" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Excited for this &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/johncarreyrou/status/1413152952294940679&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 13:37:46 GMT" tweetId="1413492575365963776" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413492575365963776" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Thank u to everyone who came to hang out with me! Congrats to all of us for making it through this year 💓 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/aaronisnotcool/status/1413324072067518473&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 04:53:35 GMT" tweetId="1413360661741150210" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413360661741150210" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 8" type="calendarDay" name="08" >
				<outline text="😰 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/paulleewr/status/1413234413337563138&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 21:38:49 GMT" tweetId="1413251247562534912" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413251247562534912" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="The producers of Queer Eye are on a nationwide search for people with crypto wallets who locked themselves out &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.castingdepot.com/p/cryptocasting&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/xs3wjhGcaJ" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 18:10:46 GMT" tweetId="1413198892812935172" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413198892812935172" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Made it to NYC hacker house TikTok &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/vikushavas/status/1413161535346823179/video/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 15:54:23 GMT" tweetId="1413164571448287234" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413164571448287234" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Any corporate brand people up for chatting with me about TikTok's new resume feature? Please DM me if so! Would love to hear from companies if they do or don't plan to leverage this &lt;a href=&quot;https://newsroom.tiktok.com/en-us/find-a-job-with-tiktok-resumes&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 14:12:24 GMT" tweetId="1413138907005284363" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413138907005284363" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="How are we supposed to get work done today with links like this floating around!? &lt;a href=&quot;https://slate.com/human-interest/2021/07/cat-person-kristen-roupenian-viral-story-about-me.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 13:38:26 GMT" tweetId="1413130356589350917" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413130356589350917" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is a really shocking story and good reminder of how many of us take clean air for granted &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/charlesornstein/status/1413089716635947008&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 11:28:15 GMT" tweetId="1413097596244144132" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413097596244144132" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="IG meme pages literally devolving into that Matt Bors comic &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1413093822091911170/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 11:13:15 GMT" tweetId="1413093822091911170" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413093822091911170" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Weird! Some of these pages are the ones who ran Bloomberg sponcon too. If anyone else notices big traditional meme pages shifting into politicized content please send to me. Would be interested in looking into &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/shawnragell/status/1413219797366566912&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 19:53:38 GMT" tweetId="1413224777792331781" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413224777792331781" inReplyToId="1413093822091911170" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="I'm old enough to remember when this account just reposted months old tweets like &quot;can you marry pizza&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1413538320173391886/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 16:39:32 GMT" tweetId="1413538320173391886" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413538320173391886" inReplyToId="1413224777792331781" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
						</outline>
					</outline>
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 7" type="calendarDay" name="07" >
				<outline text="I post a lot on here if you think of it as a social media site I guess, but I consider Twitter a chat room" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 03:11:08 GMT" tweetId="1412972491795013632" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412972491795013632" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Ice gets it &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/finallevel/status/1202360515298758656&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 03:54:37 GMT" tweetId="1412983434725756933" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412983434725756933" inReplyToId="1412972491795013632" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					<outline text="Lol &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1413172477161844744/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 16:25:48 GMT" tweetId="1413172477161844744" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413172477161844744" inReplyToId="1412972491795013632" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Read @bettinamak on “hot girl food” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vice.com/en/article/4avqpj/why-is-tinned-fish-hot-girl-food-now&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/3tloIL9GO5" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 03:08:34 GMT" tweetId="1412971847126237186" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412971847126237186" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Someone mentioned @edzitron “the substacker” to me today which means he is officially a Newsletter Guy on here" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 02:33:25 GMT" tweetId="1412963001422974980" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412963001422974980" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I love @CreatorsDigest, a 2x a week rundown featuring industry news, company hires, and deep dives on certain influencers. Shout out @shardulgo for putting it together! &lt;a href=&quot;https://creatorsdigest.substack.com/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 00:57:07 GMT" tweetId="1412938765207748608" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412938765207748608" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text=".@KaitlynFehr00 on Tana's new “influencer agency.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://berkeleybeacon.com/tana-mongeaus-dizzy-history-of-youtube-controversy/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 00:54:36 GMT" tweetId="1412938130978705409" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412938130978705409" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text=".@adamlashinsky on the creator boom &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businessinsider.com/what-could-go-wrong-with-creator-economy-boom-2021-6&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 00:48:31 GMT" tweetId="1412936600829497347" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412936600829497347" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="&quot;Thousands of would-be pop stars mailed demo tapes in a time before streaming, but the record labels didn’t get to sell ads against them. Tech giants benefit massively from the infinite number of hopefuls entering the fray&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wired.com/story/twitch-turns-10-creator-economy/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; by @cecianasta" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 00:47:14 GMT" tweetId="1412936277343842304" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412936277343842304" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Many of these are great but if I may be so bold as to add a few more....! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thecut.com/2021/07/newsletter-writers-on-their-favorite-newsletters.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 00:04:36 GMT" tweetId="1412925550558056450" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412925550558056450" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text=".@Lucas_Shaw's Screentime is essential reading on tech, entertainment, and online creators  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/account/newsletters/screentime&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 00:05:16 GMT" tweetId="1412925715507449857" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412925715507449857" inReplyToId="1412925550558056450" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
