				<outline text="These fake livestreams are becoming way too common. Seen several of influencers like Charli, Addison etc as well. They usually choose really personal Lives (a popular one is one where Charli is crying), also the watermelon rubber band guy. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/nickabouzeid/status/1412267091177136131&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 06 Jul 2021 11:19:16 GMT" tweetId="1412370557887209472" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412370557887209472" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
