				<outline text="“Ivermectin, the authors added, ‘is not a viable option to treat COVID-19.” Yet proponents of the drug’s “holy war has taken on new vigor as prominent members of the ‘Intellectual Dark Web’ have begun advocating for the drug” Good breakdown by @annamerlan &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vice.com/en/article/y3d5gv/ivermectin-covid-treatment-advocates-rogan-weinstein-hecker&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 05 Jul 2021 23:51:31 GMT" tweetId="1412197482050867200" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412197482050867200" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Ivermectin, as @annamerlan reports, has become a flashpoint to many in the anti-media crowd &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vice.com/en/article/y3d5gv/ivermectin-covid-treatment-advocates-rogan-weinstein-hecker&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/PUi1EOyOf5" type="tweet" created="Mon, 05 Jul 2021 23:54:06 GMT" tweetId="1412198130045554688" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412198130045554688" inReplyToId="1412197482050867200" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Artists have begun sharing their work under the hashtag #FixTheAlgorithm to critique the perceived lack of distribution art gets in the feed. h/t @willgonyer &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/bugdotpng/status/1412075956890648586&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 05 Jul 2021 23:45:04 GMT" tweetId="1412195856606957572" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412195856606957572" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="TikTok star Swavy aka Babyfaces has died at age of 18. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tiktok.com/@babyface.s?_d=secCgYIASAHKAESMgowwwr4kNzYNEtJcWXfGbdlJvYExepUv3hEjXiuQ5937TgUXIc7lU8QsAuxRAyHY9L2GgA%3D&amp;checksum=01c55bddbac80b0d4181bc3be1a02c6d82b91afff3223097b495984d23ba762d&amp;language=en&amp;sec_uid=MS4wLjABAAAAqXmC8UrKiGYi3jWkfvcU5Ahp1twri7ZqkUhSJ1ebcH1ymyZiNdZe0bu5c5kWdsCI&amp;sec_user_id=MS4wLjABAAAA4BgIbw0ed4-DdJrkIGl8b-Z7qVcLSeJC8LSb_o3Q8_UKKEk1hoyPyATFAQmpe-Go&amp;share_app_id=1233&amp;share_author_id=6798237097989030918&amp;share_link_id=21ABDA18-F232-44B9-8E0D-93219792C726&amp;tt_from=copy&amp;u_code=6dc3cefl1fi8a&amp;user_id=144377784793104384&amp;utm_campaign=client_share&amp;utm_medium=ios&amp;utm_source=copy&amp;source=h5_m&amp;_r=1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/MNaoyz1Gn1" type="tweet" created="Mon, 05 Jul 2021 22:12:25 GMT" tweetId="1412172541284790273" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412172541284790273" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Local news is reporting that Swavy aka Matima Miller was identified as the victim of a Monday morning homicide &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/crime/2021/07/06/swavy-death-dancing-tiktok-star-babyface-s-shooting-victim-wilmington-delaware/7872252002/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 06 Jul 2021 17:03:10 GMT" tweetId="1412457103252508673" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412457103252508673" inReplyToId="1412172541284790273" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="As usual, creators have begun ripping Swavy's final posts to IG Stories and the IG Stories of his friends/family to repackage his &quot;last moments&quot; as content for YouTube &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TaylorLorenz/status/1412457734931365888/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 06 Jul 2021 17:05:40 GMT" tweetId="1412457734931365888" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1412457734931365888" inReplyToId="1412457103252508673" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
							<outline text="This unfortunately says everything about Wendy and who and what TV media pays attention to and nothing about Swavy, who was very much a star in his own right. Really hard to watch &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/rach_greenspan/status/1413560217887989769&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 20:07:33 GMT" tweetId="1413590667385782274" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1413590667385782274" inReplyToId="1412457734931365888" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
							</outline>
