				<outline text="Are you a print reader? Donate your extra stacks of clean papers to the @wildbirdfund! https://t.co/rHkmSOXCI0" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:14:22 GMT" tweetId="1409560821546450944" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409560821546450944" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="You get a term sheet https://t.co/g6Pd6EceLd" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:05:55 GMT" tweetId="1409558694778392579" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409558694778392579" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Ppl need to understand that &quot;exposing/deep dive&quot; videos almost universally have an agenda, where things are twisted to fit a narrative and all &quot;evidence&quot; is in service of promoting that narrative. These videos mimic the language of reporting but are nothing like actual journalism https://t.co/obZr4PY181" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 16:51:35 GMT" tweetId="1409555085827268609" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409555085827268609" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="I'd say generally don't trust anything you watch on YouTube. It's a lead distributor of conspiracy theories, propaganda, and disinfo. Try to read a book on the topic by an expert or go to verified sources like a reputable news outlet or expert in the space https://t.co/8Ew3dazGUF" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:01:09 GMT" tweetId="1409557493655638021" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409557493655638021" inReplyToId="1409555085827268609" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="Way too many young people blindly trust things they've seen on YouTube the way too many boomers trust everything they read on FB" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:13:07 GMT" tweetId="1409560506365472768" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409560506365472768" inReplyToId="1409557493655638021" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
